{"tid":1850373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日三間公立醫院共有90名護士請病假","createTime":"2020-01-29T13:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T17:41:37.000Z","uid":125168,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f206c8caf06982f5cad4dfbd14dfa15d33be0331","tid":1850373,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"三間公立醫院共有90名護士請病假<br />\n7分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】博愛、東區及瑪嘉烈醫院今日總共有90名護士請病假。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局指，博愛醫院手術室今日有26名護士請病假，醫院日前已檢視非緊急服務及調節服務量，包括非緊急手術，所以手術室服務不受影響<br />\n<br />\n而東區醫院手術室及深切治療部，分別有26名及15名護士請病假，醫院指已因應情況調配人手，24小時緊急手術及病房服務維持正常。<br />\n<br />\n瑪嘉烈醫院亦有23名護士請病假，經調配人手，病房服務不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局指，各醫院感染控制組跟進職員是否涉及集體感染，人事部門會根據既定程序處理病假。"},{"pid":"574b926b5b5cfac3c2939dfb6b0249f451644e6a","tid":1850373,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"佢哋會調配人手㗎啦，醫護正式罷工前請集體請病假"},{"pid":"8df126eb682473edcdeaab48f0edb513e09994f1","tid":1850373,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929f8f85a2bb69cfe1e0c21edccb38963b278f61","tid":1850373,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】3公院90護士今請病假促港府封關：不能白白送死<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2vydWuN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vydWuN&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHxSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=7790d862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2vydWuN</a>"},{"pid":"78b108d390e32c6e5b19b6b74c09b20b137ebe2f","tid":1850373,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c767d369c3b2976a5bcb495b13af83581ff735aa","tid":1850373,"uid":108337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"藍絲一個頂10個，唔驚"},{"pid